column5: I have no idea what you're talkin' about me Brudder. Good tune though.

Tryin' to get even eh Bubba?  ... that's a dang good tune, and more true than you realize!!!   ... if I was Canuckian and used to the cold... I'd be there reguardless!!!    ... deer season is for the folks that aren't worth a crap at fishing... like you!!!
